273
00:39:31,125 --> 00:39:34,833
Huo Feng, Huo Feng...

274
00:39:47,333 --> 00:39:49,125
Help!

275
00:40:03,125 --> 00:40:08,583
Huo Feng, help!

276
00:40:11,208 --> 00:40:15,917
Old Lin, Old Lin.

277
00:40:28,792 --> 00:40:30,167
Old Lin.

278
00:40:55,542 --> 00:40:56,667
Old Lin.

279
00:41:25,958 --> 00:41:27,250
Old Lin.

