00:41:36,458 --> 00:41:37,958
Old Lin.

281
00:41:39,333 --> 00:41:40,833
Where are you?

282
00:41:44,125 --> 00:41:47,250
What the hell are you doing?

283
00:41:47,250 --> 00:41:50,042
Did you hear Lao Lin cry for help?
