295
00:42:49,375 --> 00:42:52,250
I recorded it a few hours before he died.

296
00:42:53,833 --> 00:42:55,500
That's it...

297
00:42:56,333 --> 00:42:58,167
a bad omen.

298
00:42:59,375 --> 00:43:01,000
