328
00:45:39,417 --> 00:45:40,500
Cut.

329
00:45:43,792 --> 00:45:45,125
How is it?

330
00:45:46,542 --> 00:45:47,750
Look.

331
00:45:48,292 --> 00:45:49,292
What did you say?

332
00:45:49,292 --> 00:45:52,250
The act is too bad. You go and talk to her.

333
00:45:52,250 --> 00:45:54,125
Come... put it on.

334
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:57,083
