335
00:45:58,208 --> 00:46:01,792
This is a precious key your father
left behind for you,

336
00:46:02,833 --> 00:46:04,417
This is a relic.

337
00:46:04,875 --> 00:46:07,250
Not to pick up purses.

338
00:46:08,500 --> 00:46:11,292
Fix her makeup, I said fix her makeup.

339
00:46:14,250 --> 00:46:17,917
I said let's do the next shot, right?

340
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:20,125
Producer?

341
