- Be careful..

363
00:47:37,250 --> 00:47:39,000
Please go.

364
00:47:40,125 --> 00:47:42,458
Is that golden Buddha wanted by the upper class?

365
00:47:42,458 --> 00:47:46,042
Right. They asked for this.

366
00:47:46,750 --> 00:47:50,333
